ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectPolar Medal and Sovereign's Medal for Volunteers Order
PrecisOrder (1) directing that the POLAR MEDAL shall follow the EUROPEAN SECURITY AND DEFENCE POLICY SERVICE MEDAL in the order of precedence in the Canadian Honours System; and (2) directing that the SOVEREIGN'S MEDAL FOR VOLUNTEERS shall follow the POLAR MEDAL in the order of precedence in the Canadian Honours System.
